tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE survey_data ( 
    id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    respondent_id INT, 
    survey_question TEXT, 
    survey_answer TEXT 
)

CREATE TABLE external_tools ( 
    tool_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    tool_name TEXT, 
    integration_type TEXT, 
    documentation_link TEXT 
)

CREATE TABLE dashboard_data ( 
    dashboard_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    dashboard_name TEXT, 
    visualization_type TEXT, 
    dashboard_url TEXT 
)

CREATE TABLE visualization_tools (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
tool_name TEXT,
version TEXT,
url TEXT);

CREATE TABLE dashboard_data (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
dashboard_name TEXT,
description TEXT,
owner TEXT);

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
survey_id INT REFERENCES survey_data(id),
respondent_name TEXT,
response_date TIMESTAMP);

CREATE TABLE visualization_data (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
tool_id INT REFERENCES visualization_tools(id),
dashboard_id INT REFERENCES dashboard_data(id),
data_source TEXT,
visualization_type TEXT);
